      "raw_text": "QUINCY, Wash, Jan. ARMED\ncitizens yesterday confiscated a\nGreat Northern boxcar containing\n90 tons of coal. The train pulled\ninto the yards at 6 O'Clock. Its ar\nrival was heralded with pistol shots\nwhich summoned about 80 citizens,\nall armed. Some climbed into the\ncab of the engine and at the point\nof revOlvers forced the engineer\nand trainmen to cut out the car of\ncoal. The coal was divided among\nresidents after the train proceeded."
    }
